Drone
========

Motivation
----------
This is a firmware for a drone.

Installation
------------
Run following command to get the source code:

	git clone git://s55969da3.adsl.online.nl/drone/firmware.git

Now you have to go inside the folder:

	cd firmware

Now goto https://developer.arm.com/open-source/gnu-toolchain/gnu-rm/downloads to download the tool chain and unzip it to this folder. Then run following command to compile:

	make all

To clean the build:

  make clean
